snippet.title: Amber & Noah Clare/Jennifer Kesse Updates
snippet.description:
You can support this channel by donating here:
https://www.paypal.me/aimeesaurusrex


Amber Clare (16) was abducted in Kentucky and Noah Clare (3) was abducted in Tennessee.  They were reported missing November 7, 2021.  They are believed to be with Jake Clare.  He is reportedly driving a silver 2005 Subaru Legacy wagon.  There is a dent in rear drivers side bumper and stickers on the back.  If you have any information, please call 1-800-TBI-Find. 

Jennifer Kesse's parents are still actively searching for their daughter.  Jennifer went missing in Orlando over 15 years ago.  

https://www.gofundme.com/f/kasmv-help-us-find-jennifer-kesse

https://radio.foxnews.com/podcast/broken-dreams/

💥 Chad Daybell has no chin. ♾
